				\begin{document}$$e=\Delta r$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M146"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>e</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mml:mi><mml:mi>r</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5627_Article_IEq62.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>) from 0 to 0.1. Finally, we varied the number of studies (<inline-formula id="IEq63"><alternatives><tex-math id="M147">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
