				\begin{document}$$K$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M174"><mml:mi>K</mml:mi></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5627_Article_IEq75.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> = 5) and keeping RR to 1.30 (or 1/1.30). Third, we only varied RR from 1.05 to 1.30 (or 1/1.05 to 1.30) while keeping MAF to 0.1 and the number of studies to 5 (<inline-formula id="IEq76"><alternatives><tex-math id="M175">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
