				\begin{document}$$p$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M128"><mml:mi>p</mml:mi></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5627_Article_IEq52.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. Assuming a very low prevalence, the expected case MAF becomes <inline-formula id="IEq53"><alternatives><tex-math id="M129">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
