    </sec>
    <sec id="Sec17">
      <title>PASTRY achieves similar power to the splitting approach</title>
      <p id="Par37">We evaluated the power of PASTRY in a variety of situations, while varying minor allele frequency (MAF), relative risk (RR), and the number of studies (<inline-formula id="IEq72"><alternatives><tex-math id="M167">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
