				\begin{document}$${n}_{-}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M126"><mml:msub><mml:mi>n</mml:mi><mml:mo>-</mml:mo></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5627_Article_IEq51.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> controls and all controls were shared among studies. We assumed a variant with a MAF of <inline-formula id="IEq52"><alternatives><tex-math id="M127">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
